      "description": "Roll up your sleeves for a fantastic opportunity! This vehicle is the perfect project for a DIY enthusiast or someone looking for a budget-friendly entry into car ownership. While it currently requires significant mechanical and cosmetic attention to get it back into top shape, it offers a solid foundation and a lot of potential for those willing to put in the work!",
