      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting an impeccable exterior finish and an interior that retains its original factory luster. Every mechanical component has been rigorously inspected to ensure peak performance, mirroring the experience of a new delivery. For the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a truly pristine asset.",
